[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Ablack-highlighter-theme/black-highlighter-logo.svg]]

+ Usage

++ Note: This is a Black Highlighter based theme. You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme as well in order to use this theme. [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|To learn more go here]]].

This is a BHL version of [[[theme:broken-masquerade|Broken Masquerade Theme]]] by Cyantreuse and [[*user stormbreath]]. It is designed to be used for the [[[broken-masquerade-hub|Broken Masquerade Canon]]].

On any wiki:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:expose]]@@
[[/div]]

If you would not like to use the police flashing lights on the header, add the following code in anywhere of your article:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[module css]]@@
@@div#extra-div-1,div#extra-div-2{display:none;}@@
@@[[/module]]@@
[[/div]]

+ Examples

[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Abroken-masquerade/new_scp_logo.png|caption=New SCP Logo by Cyantreuse|width=200px]]

A horizontal rule can be created with 5 hyphens "@@-----@@" and extends across the whole page if it's not placed inside anything (eg a blockquote). The lines separating sections of this document are horizontal rules.

-----

Titles can be created by putting between one and six plus "+" at the start of the line

[[collapsible show="+ Titles" hide="- Titles"]]
